  "title": "Service Coordinator  (3 months contract)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Service Coordinator (3 months contract)</strong></u></p><ul><li> Coordinate with service contractors and customers to schedule service appointments.</li><li>Handle customer enquiries through multiple channels, including phone calls, emails, Live Chat, WhatsApp, and walk-in customers, ensuring timely and professional responses.</li><li>Compilation and preparation of Reports to the Management.</li><li>Any other duties as assigned by the Service Manager</li></ul><p>REQUIREMENTS</p><ul><li>Diploma in Business Administration, or similar discipline</li><li>Minimum 1 years of relevant after-sales customer service experience.</li><li>Good analytical, organizational, and documentation skills.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Excel.</li><li>Able to work independently and communicate effectively with internal and external stakeholders.</li></ul><p> We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidate will be notify.</p><p>EA License No : 18C9228 REG No : R1324979 (Woo Kum Yoke)</p>",
